<item>
            <title>[PIG-403] Porting of the slicer into types branch caused all scripts to run just one map.</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-403</link>
                <project id="12310730" key="PIG">Pig</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;In PigSlicer.java, splittable is set to false by default.  This causes the system to scan an entire file in a single map.  It should be set to true by default, so that files are only scanned in a single map if the user explicitly requests it.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
